reviewText:
This is a fantastic series. I follow it religiously and its part of my viewing lineup at least twice a week! I'm watching and waiting for Season 2.
Keep it coming!

Body Jumpers is a fantastic series! I follow it adamantly, I enjoy everything about the series from all the characters to the various storylines, and the special effects, I give it a 5 star rating because it continues to get better each episode! The actors and actresses who star in the series work very hard at what they do and it shows! The creator of the series is on top of his "A" game as he leaves you begging for more ...I look forward to see what the jumpers will be doing next! Keep up the great work everyone!----- Baker
